"26:205:3" : {s: 26, a: 205, w: 3, r: "متع", t: "مَّتَّعْنَٰهُمْ", l: "مَّتَّعْ", lc: 18, tl: "mattaʿnāhum", lb: "জীবিকা দেওয়া, উপভোগ করতে দেয়া, উপকৃত করা",e: "We let them enjoy", b: "আমি তাদেরকে ভোগ্যবস্তু দিয়েছি", i: "Kami beri kesenangan mereka", f: 1, rm: "to enjoy/benefit, gift, anything useful/advantageous, goods (e.g. utensils, furniture), a commodity."},
